<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Assignment</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #3b82f6; color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { background: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-top: none; }
    .footer { background: #f9fafb; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #3b82f6; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .info-box { background: #eff6ff; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
    h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ðŸ“‹ New Assignment</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <strong>{{staffName}}</strong>,</p>
      
      <p>You have been assigned to review a partnership request.</p>
      
      <div class="info-box">
        <p><strong>Reference ID:</strong> {{requestId}}</p>
        <p><strong>Organization:</strong> {{orgName}}</p>
        <p><strong>Event Title:</strong> {{eventTitle}}</p>
        <p><strong>Requested Date:</strong> {{eventDate}}</p>
        <p><strong>Hub:</strong> {{hubName}}</p>
        <p><strong>Status:</strong> Under Review</p>
      </div>
      
      <a href="{{app_url}}/dashboard/requests/{{requestId}}" class="button">View Request Details</a>
      
      <p>Please review the request and take appropriate action within 48 hours.</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br><strong>ALX Partnership System</strong></p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{current_year}} ALX Africa. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
